                                        <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"> </i> &nbsp;	Data analysis with  <b>SPHINX</b> 	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<b> Dr. Younès BOUGHZALA</b><br>
                                        <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"> </i> &nbsp;	Analysis of data <b>PLS vs AMOS</b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<b> Pr. Fathi AKROUT</b>
                                        </font></p>

